<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">The user can use this application to request a Truck to be dispatched at the place and date specified by the user according to the method specified by our company, whereas we will pick up the Truck company (Hereinafter referred to as "Truck dispatch service").&nbsp;However, the user must not make a dispatch request corresponding to each of the following items, and if we determine that the dispatch request by the user falls under any of the following items, or a Truck of a Truck company desired by the user If there is no inventory (the number of Trucks determined by the Truck company to be able to pick up the vehicle according to the request for dispatch by the Truck company at the time of the dispatch request), our company will May not provide Truck dispatching services.&nbsp;In addition, if the user gets on a Truck different from the Truck requested to dispatch, or if the Truck requested to arrive at the place specified by the user, the Truck specified by the user for a certain period of time If it does not appear, it can be considered that the dispatch request has been cancelled.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">(1) Request for dispatch to a place other than the area designated by each Truck company</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">(2) Vehicle dispatch request in a manner that violates these Terms of Use</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">(3) Vehicle dispatch request from a person who has violated these Terms of Service in the past</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">(4) At the time of dispatch request, the dispatch request when the user has not yet settled the Truck fare (defined in 2.3) when he or she used the Internet payment service in the past five times or more.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">(5) A dispatch request in which a double dispatch is suspected (it means that the same user makes multiple dispatch requests at substantially the same time).</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">(6) Dispatch request containing false content</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">(7) A dispatch request from a Truck company if there is a request from the Truck company to reject the dispatch request from a specific user</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">(8) Multiple cancellations in the past (regardless of whether or not the Truck company or our company has been contacted in advance or for any reason, the Truck was actually dispatched based on the user's dispatch request The same applies to the following.)</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">(9) Other dispatch requests that we deem inappropriate</p>
<h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); margin: 20px 0px 15px; font-size: 18px; padding: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">2.2.2. Priority dispatch request function</h5>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">When the user pays the fee specified by the Company (hereinafter referred to as “priority dispatch request fee”) using the Internet settlement service specified in 3., (i) reserves the dispatch request preferentially. And (ii) priority dispatch request can be made immediately (hereinafter referred to as "priority dispatch request function").&nbsp;If a user makes a vehicle allocation request using the priority vehicle allocation request function (hereinafter referred to as “priority vehicle allocation request”), we shall request the Truck company to pick up a vehicle according to the priority vehicle allocation request. You.&nbsp;In this case, the provisions of 2.2.1.&nbsp;In addition, the user's obligation to pay the priority vehicle allocation request fee shall be incurred when the vehicle allocation determination specified in 2.3. (3) is made based on the priority vehicle allocation request.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); margin: 40px 0px 15px; font-size: 18px; padding: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">2.2.3. Pre-determined fare function</h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Only when using the Internet payment service specified in 3., the user requests the vehicle to be dispatched on the route and fare determined in advance on this application (hereinafter referred to as “predetermined fare”) (hereinafter “ Pre-determined fare function ").&nbsp;Each time a user makes a vehicle allocation request using the pre-determined fare function, the user must agree to the following on the consent screen of this application (note that the consent screen will not be displayed in the future. The user who has selected will be deemed to have agreed to the following items in advance each time he / she makes a dispatch request using the pre-determined fare function.)</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">(1) If you change the route during driving due to the convenience of the user, you will need to pay the pre-determined fare at the time of ordering, and travel from the point of change at the meter fare (time and distance combined system).</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">(2) The amount of the pre-determined fare may be higher than the meter fare or the fixed fare when the road is empty.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">(3) If the designated time does not appear at the place specified by the user even after a certain period of time from the estimated arrival time, the pre-determined fare will be canceled and switched to the meter fare or canceled.</p>
<h4 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); margin: 40px 0px 15px; font-size: 18px; padding: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">2.3. Provision of passenger transportation services and payment of fares by Truck companies</h4>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">The User shall confirm the following matters regarding the provision of the passenger transportation service from the Truck company.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">(1) In connection with the provision of Truck dispatch service by our company, if a Truck company picks up a car in response to a request from the user and provides a passenger transport service to the user by the Truck company, You shall receive the Passenger Carriage Service in your name and at your own expense and responsibility.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">(2) Regarding the fare, standby fee, pick-up fee, highway fee, parking fee, sightseeing guide fee, and other passenger transportation service fees to be paid by the user (hereinafter referred to as "Truck fee"), each Truck company The user shall pay the Truck fare to each Truck company in accordance with the instructions of each Truck company.&nbsp;However, if the user uses the Internet payment service based on these Terms of Use, the Truck fare and the user will use the priority dispatch request function in accordance with the provisions of 3. “Use of Internet Payment Service”. The priority dispatch request fee (hereinafter collectively referred to as “Truck fare, etc.”) shall be paid.&nbsp;In addition, with respect to the pre-determined fare, the user shall pay the Truck fare set by us based on the fare system set by each Truck company and the coefficient set by the Transportation Bureau through the Internet settlement service used based on these terms and conditions .&nbsp;Notwithstanding the above, if we specify, we may accept such Truck fares on behalf of the Truck company.</p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(25, 47, 96); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans USAese&quot;, &quot;ヒラギノ角ゴ Pro W3&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro&quot;, メイリオ, Meiryo, Osaka, &quot;ＭＳ Ｐゴシック&quot;, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">(3) If the user cancels after deciding the dispatch, the method of designating the reservation fee, pick-up fee, initial fare and other fees (hereinafter referred to as "cancellation fee") specified by each Truck company. And pay to each Truck company.&nbsp;However, if the user uses the Internet payment service based on these Terms of Use, the cancellation fee and the user's use of the priority dispatch request function in accordance with the provisions of 3. A priority dispatch request fee (hereinafter collectively referred to as “cancellation fee, etc.”) shall be paid.&nbsp;Notwithstanding the foregoing, if we specify, we may accept such cancellation fees on behalf of the Truck company.&nbsp;In addition, in these Terms of Service, the dispatch decision means the time when the user is notified of the estimated arrival time on the order completion screen of this application.</p>
